    <Company>Waher Data AB</Company>
    <Product>Waher.IoTGateway</Product>
    <Description>Command-line tool that helps you analyze the difference in clocks between machines compatible with the IEEE XMPP IoT extensions.</Description>
    <Copyright>Copyright Â© Waher Data AB 2018-2019. All rights reserved.</Copyright>
    <PackageLicenseUrl></PackageLicenseUrl>
